review: Visited hospital for root canal treatment, Dr chandrashekhar garu explained the issue and the procedure in easy manner.It's very much comfortable and affordable. I recommend doctor for sure for any dental issues.

****** ** ** ***** Has lot of patience and his experience made him so calm and composed. He does the job less traumatic. Very less dentists in Hyd who has 21 years of exp. Great work sir. Will definitely recommend him to friends and family.
